{"tid":2121872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對源頭不明的感染者有所推測","createTime":"2020-07-23T15:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T16:31:44.000Z","uid":26770,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"db98804761256f75a7c2abecfd83640370a4674f","tid":2121872,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T15:07:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2118999/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2118999/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n張竹君有意隱瞞真相<br />\n所謂源頭不明實際係一講完就政治不正確<br />\n<br />\n1 帝制派慶71淪陷的一大堆活動<br />\n2保安局李家超為阻礙選舉出左20萬張證比中國人直落香港不需隔離,目的係爆瘟疫就停選舉,用現有議會抽光庫房所有錢"},{"pid":"f6c829c41748b5a436a4c1257070125c3175152f","tid":2121872,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T15:08:59.000Z","msg":"支那大爆發: 睇下港共豁免左邊32類人士免受強制檢疫<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fFftuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fFftuS</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（搵到第三波零號病人）內河碼頭有不少獲豁免檢疫的船員進出<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2116184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2116184</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H78LR7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH78LR7a.jpg&h=78d326f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f0726541871829f0ad4343a2884e3bf415932dd","tid":2121872,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T15:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746c699769c554efa308e900482da3c8391fb625","tid":2121872,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T15:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8103edd0f613d632dbe668f0b17a3d0051c4d10f","tid":2121872,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T15:50:07.000Z","msg":"大家都知，仆街正苦唔敢講，唔敢認"},{"pid":"4810c3dde79e470661f7d872bf0319e6f01149ba","tid":21